sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant BC as BuildConfig
    participant IS as ImageStream
    participant Deploy as Deployment
    participant Pod as Pod
    participant Route as Route
    participant User as End User

    Dev->>GH: Push code to master
    GH->>BC: Webhook triggers build
    BC->>BC: Clone repository
    BC->>BC: Build Docker image
    BC->>IS: Push image (Build 85)
    IS->>Deploy: ImageChange trigger
    Deploy->>Deploy: Start rolling update
    Deploy->>Pod: Create new pod
    Pod->>Pod: Container starting
    Pod->>Pod: Load secrets & mount PVC
    Pod->>Pod: Start Flask app (port 5000)
    Deploy->>Pod: Health check passes
    Deploy->>Pod: Mark as ready
    Route->>Pod: Route traffic to new pod
    Deploy->>Pod: Terminate old pod
    User->>Route: Access dashboard
    Route->>Pod: Forward HTTPS request
    Pod->>User: Return dashboard HTML
